@startuml
title Digidoclocker State Diagram

[*] --> CitizenRegistration

state CitizenRegistration
state CitizenLogin
state DocumentUpload
state ProfileView
state CertificateApplication
state CertificateReapply
state RegistrarRequest
state RegistrarReapply
state SessionEnd

CitizenRegistration --> CitizenLogin : register
CitizenLogin --> DocumentUpload : login
DocumentUpload --> ProfileView : view profile
DocumentUpload --> CertificateApplication : apply for certificate
DocumentUpload --> DocumentUpload : continue upload

CertificateApplication --> CertificateReapply : reapply
RegistrarRequest --> RegistrarReapply : continue request

CitizenLogin --> ProfileView : view profile
CitizenLogin --> CertificateApplication : apply for certificate
CitizenLogin --> DocumentUpload : upload documents

RegistrarRequest --> RegistrarReapply : continue request

DocumentUpload --> CertificateApplication : apply for certificate
DocumentUpload --> DocumentUpload : continue upload

CertificateApplication --> CertificateReapply : reapply
RegistrarRequest --> RegistrarReapply : continue request

ProfileView --> CitizenLogin : logout
CertificateApplication --> CitizenLogin : logout
CertificateReapply --> CitizenLogin : logout
RegistrarRequest --> CitizenLogin : logout
RegistrarReapply --> CitizenLogin : logout

SessionEnd --> [*]

@enduml
